05:30.920 --> 05:46.420
signed for me both as Jekyll and Hyde and I got Boris Karloff to sign as the
Frankenstein monster and the mummy. And so, the last 50 years I've wound up with

05:46.420 --> 06:00.520
125,000 stills from all of the fantastic movies ever made in the world. And 18
,000 lobby cards and uncounted thousands of clippings. I get Hollywood Reporter

06:00.520 --> 06:12.680
and Variety and Publishers Weekly and I constantly cut out everything concerning
