30:30.460 --> 30:41.240
life than the beginning, so we'll kind of cool it and get a more modest home for
the last years of our life. But I'll always want a guest room and I think I'm

30:41.240 --> 30:51.660
always going to keep several hundred really favorite things around me, my best
books. Your wife must have been very understanding through these years. Well,

30:51.660 --> 31:02.860
fortunately, she was a science fiction fan all of her life before she met up
with me, only she was a fan in French and German. And when she came to this

31:02.860 --> 31:16.480
country around 33 years ago, she gravitated toward becoming a book clerk. And
one day I walked up to her with a whole stack of books to buy and she said, may

31:16.480 --> 31:21.020
I wait on you, sir? And that was her fatal mistake. I've been doing so ever
since.

